findings.title: Typo in error message
findings.description: The withdraw() functions of TokenDistributor and StakingNapToken have a typo in the error message, ‘or’ instead of ‘and’. It is better to describe the error as it is in order to provide the best user experience to the user that receives the error.

findings.title: Unverified source of antisnipe contract
findings.description: The audit report highlights a potential vulnerability where the source of the antisnipe contract is unverified, which can lead to security risks.
